					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Okay, I've <em>temporarly</em> updated data of the last 8k PRG bank ($e000-$ffff) here <a href="http://jonathan.microclub.ch/contra/gradius2_patch.bin" class="postlink">http://jonathan.microclub.ch/contra/gradius2_patch.bin</a>.
<br />To run the game as an iNES ROM just go with an hex editor to offset $1E010, paste this (overwriting previous data), and change the header so that it is mapper 4 and not mapper 25 (so that nobody can call me illegaly distributing the ROM).
<br />I really wonder how it looks on real hardware, status bar is probably shaking, I tried change the timing a bit but I couldn't get rid of this shaking. Tell me if your ship is always destroyed as it is in Nestopia, this is really weird.</div>

