						<div class="postbody"><div class="quotetitle">MottZilla wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">I'm guessing you must have changed the CHR, cause the sprites for me are always messed up with just that 8kb prg change. If you're done with it, and not just done with it for the day, I'd love to see any notes and get a copy of where you are at. I'd like to see the first level with correct sprites.</div>
